0:00:00.020,0:00:04.140
Zita rangu ndi Blessing Iloanya. Ndinobva ku Anambra State.

0:00:04.140,0:00:05.900
Ini ndiri mushandi wehurumende.

0:00:05.900,0:00:09.980
Dambudziko rakandiunza pa SCOAN nderekuti

0:00:09.980,0:00:18.520
Ndakapindwa muropa ne kunhuhwidza ne kunwa parafini.

0:00:18.520,0:00:21.920
Ndicharatidza kuti iparafini zvechokwadi. Ndichapisa chidimbu che puranga iri.

0:00:21.920,0:00:25.220
Wawu, Mwari wangu!

0:00:25.220,0:00:26.260
Mwari wangu!

0:00:26.260,0:00:29.720
Parafini

0:00:29.720,0:00:32.400
Iparafini zvechokwadi.

0:00:32.400,0:00:35.200
Mukadzi ari pedyo neni ndi amai vangu.

0:00:35.200,0:00:39.920
Izvo zvose zvakatanga makore anenge 18 apfuura apo ndaiva kuchikoro chesekondari.

0:00:39.920,0:00:44.520
Pakanga pane rimwe zuva apo pfungwa yakauya kwandiri

0:00:44.520,0:00:48.000
kuti parafini iyi inogona kunaka, ndinofanira kuyiedza.

0:00:48.000,0:00:54.500
Saka, ndakacheka pepa, ndikarinyika muparafini ndokutanga kurifunhidza.

0:00:54.500,0:00:59.140
Kubva pakufunhidza parafini, ndakatanga kusvisvina ne kunwa.

0:00:59.140,0:01:03.980
Kubva ipapo, ndakatanga kuitora zuva rega rega.

0:01:03.980,0:01:17.840
Zvadaro, ndakaona kuti ndinakirwe nayo zvirinani, ndaifanira kunotenga mabhisikiti ndoanyika muparafini.

0:01:17.840,0:01:22.480
Vatariri, ndinovimba muri kutarisa.

0:01:22.480,0:01:27.820
Vatarisi, pasi pose, muri kuona here?

0:01:27.820,0:01:28.760
Wawu.

0:01:28.760,0:01:30.980
Mukadzi Arikudya Bisikiti Rakanyikwa Mu Parafini

0:01:30.980,0:01:31.720
Wawu.

0:01:31.720,0:01:37.580
Kana iwe uchiziva kuti mhinduro yakasvika kwauri, simudza ruoko rwako!

0:01:37.580,0:01:39.340
Yako inopfuura parafini here?

0:01:39.340,0:01:40.540
Kwete

0:01:40.540,0:01:43.760
Inowanzonaka zvikuru. Ndinoifarira kwazvo.

0:01:43.760,0:01:45.860
Ndakaedza ndoga kuti ndirege.

0:01:45.860,0:01:52.180
Ndakaedza kuchengetedza parafini kure nekwandinenge ndigere asi nguva dzose ndaizoiona,

0:01:52.180,0:01:58.660
Ndaizonyika ruoko rwangu mairi ndotanga kuinhuhwidza nekuiisa mumuromo mangu

0:01:58.660,0:02:05.080
Blessing anonyika tishu muparafini kuti aratidze kuti anofunhidza sei nekunwa.

0:02:05.080,0:02:10.280
Anoramba achisvisvina parafini yose kubva mutishu achibva amedza .

0:02:10.280,0:02:16.080
Iyi ndiyo imwe yenzira dzaanoshandisa kunwa parafini.

0:02:16.080,0:02:19.320
Ndinoitora zuva roga roga asi ndakaedza kurega ndoga;

0:02:19.320,0:02:21.660
Ndakaedza kuchengeta parafini kure nemba yangu.

0:02:21.660,0:02:23.080
Kubvira makore mangani ikozvino?

0:02:23.080,0:02:24.320
Kwemakore gumi nemasere ikozvino.

0:02:24.320,0:02:26.240
Wakaedza zvose.

0:02:26.240,0:02:29.960
Hungu, ndakaedza ndoga; Ndakanyengetera asi hazvina kushanda.

0:02:29.960,0:02:33.640
Munhu wa Mwari, zvakakanganisa hupenyu hwangu nenzira dzakawanda.

0:02:33.640,0:02:36.920
Kazhinji kacho pandinoitora, mudumbu mangu munorwadza.

0:02:36.920,0:02:39.680
Ndaizotanga kuenda kuchimbudzi kakawanda.

0:02:39.680,0:02:44.480
Uye zvakare upenyu hwangu huzere nezvinetso uye zvipingamupinyi.

0:02:44.480,0:02:46.920
Ndiani ane Anointing Water?

0:02:46.920,0:02:49.160
Murume anouya mberi.

0:02:49.160,0:02:51.320
Iwe ingotarisa.

0:02:51.320,0:02:57.820
Muzita ra Jesu Kristu we Nazareta, ndinokurayira buda kunze, muzita ra Jesu!

0:02:57.820,0:03:03.940
Iwe mweya wekuuraya, kuba nekuparadza, muzita ra Jesu Kristu, buda!

0:03:03.940,0:03:05.360
Jesu mukuru kudarika iwe!

0:03:05.360,0:03:07.060
Buda, muzita ra Jesu!

0:03:07.060,0:03:10.560
Buda, muzita ra Jesu Kristu!

0:03:10.560,0:03:12.140
Iye zvino, asununguka.

0:03:12.140,0:03:17.280
Asununguka Mu Zita ra Jesu

0:03:17.280,0:03:20.540
Chii chaitika paanga achipfapfaidza Anointing Water?

0:03:20.540,0:03:24.360
Ndanga ndichinzwa mamwe manzwiro mukati mangu.

0:03:24.360,0:03:31.440
Blessing anotora tishu orinyika kamwe zvakare muparafini kuitira kuti aone kana anunurwa zvechokwadi.

0:03:31.440,0:03:34.840
Kuna Mwari ngakuve ne kubwinya! Blessing adzikinurwa pekupedzisira!

0:03:34.840,0:03:40.840
Asununguka Mu Zita ra Jesu

0:03:40.840,0:03:45.260
Munoziva munhu chaiye izvi ndizvo zvinofanirwa kuitika.

0:03:45.260,0:03:47.740
Kana iwe waenda kumba ikozvino, kana ukatora parafini,

0:03:47.740,0:03:51.580
kunyange iwe ukanzwa kunhuhwa kwe parafini, iwe uchakosora.

0:03:51.580,0:03:54.280
Uyu munhu chaiye zvino.

0:03:54.280,0:03:55.860
Chii chakaitika?

0:03:55.860,0:03:57.060
Iri kundisvota.

0:03:57.060,0:03:59.120
Zvakanaka, chii chaitika apo wanga uchikosora?

0:03:59.120,0:04:01.360
Kusvotwa ikoko ndiko kuri kuita kuti ndikosore.

0:04:01.360,0:04:05.720
Akanga achiinwa kwemakore 18 apfuura uye aive asingambokosora.

0:04:05.720,0:04:12.560
Ishoma yaabva kutora ikozvino, ari kuirutsa izvo zvinofanirwa kuita munhu chaiye.

0:04:12.560,0:04:16.000
Izvozvo zvinoratidza kuti mukadzi uyu akanga asiri munhu chaiye kare.

0:04:16.000,0:04:19.640
Ari kungoita izvo munhu chaiye anofanirwa iye zvino.

0:04:19.640,0:04:20.980
Urikuona here?

0:04:20.980,0:04:24.040
Chii chiri kuitika kwauri?

0:04:24.040,0:04:28.360
Haisisina manakiro akanaka zvakare. Ndinovenga manzwiro acho.

0:04:28.360,0:04:32.540
Muviri wangu unosvotwa.

0:04:32.540,0:04:35.820
Mbiri kuna Mwari! Blessing anunurwa pakupedzisira.

0:04:35.820,0:04:41.240
Anoshandisa sipo yekugeza maoko kuti abvise parafini mumaoko ake.

0:04:41.240,0:04:44.800
Kuruboshwe, tinoona kubvira kweparafini chaiyo -

0:04:44.800,0:04:49.360
chinhu icho Blessing akanga akapindwa nacho muropa, kwemakore 18.

0:04:49.360,0:04:56.780
Kurudyi, Blessing anoshandisa sipo yekugeza mukanwa kuti abvise manzwiro ave kumusvota ikozvino mushure me dzikinuro yake.

0:04:56.780,0:05:01.320
Kuruboshwe, taonawo kuratidzwa kwemaitiro akasiyana

0:05:01.320,0:05:06.080
Blessing aisimbonwa parafini zuva nezuva.

0:05:06.080,0:05:11.940
Kuifunhidza zvikuru kwazvo ne tishu ne kuinwa nguva nenguva zvakare.

0:05:11.940,0:05:15.840
kusvikira parafini yose yanyatsobudiswa mariri zvachose.

0:05:15.840,0:05:21.780
Ainyikawo mabhisikiti mu parafini kuti anyevenutse bisikiti ne parafini

0:05:21.780,0:05:25.260
uye ozoridya pasina kana kutya.

0:05:25.260,0:05:31.360
Idzi ndidzo dzimwe dze nzira dzaakange achidya nadzo parafini kwemakore 18 apfuura.

0:05:31.360,0:05:33.840
Zvechokwadi, izvi zvakanga zvisiri izvo zvinofanirwa.

0:05:33.840,0:05:36.760
Iri ndiro basa remweya yakaipa.

0:05:36.760,0:05:43.060
Asi kuna Mwari kuve ne kubwinya, iye akagamuchira ruponeso rwake uye tsika yake inotyisa yemakore 18

0:05:43.060,0:05:49.080
yekunhuhwidza ne kunwa parafini yakasvitswa kumagumo ne muvambi wehupenyu - Jesu Kristu!

0:05:49.080,0:05:53.740
CHAPUPU CHINOENDERERA

0:05:53.740,0:05:56.320
Mangwanani akanaka, Chechi!

0:05:56.320,0:06:04.620
Zita rangu ndi Blessing Ezekwudo uye murume akamira parutivi rwangu murume wangu

0:06:04.620,0:06:11.840
uye kasikana kaduku mwanasikana wangu Akuchi.

0:06:11.840,0:06:15.060
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:06:15.060,0:06:19.380
Mukadzi wamaona uko aiva ini.

0:06:19.380,0:06:24.420
Makore matanhatu apfuura, ndakanga ndakapindwa muropa nekufunhidza ne kunwa parafini.

0:06:24.420,0:06:27.180
Zvakanga zvakashata zvokuti kunyange pandaienda kumwe,

0:06:27.180,0:06:32.580
Ndaizoda kumhanya ndichidzokera kumba kuitira kuti ndirambe ndichienderera mberi nemabasa angu.

0:06:32.580,0:06:35.220
Kazhinji kacho, kufunhidza kwaive kusina kukwana.

0:06:35.220,0:06:39.520
Ndaizoda kuinwa uye ndaizoda chimwe chinhu chaiendera nayo.

0:06:39.520,0:06:43.780
Ndaizoenda kunotenga mabhisikiti. Ndainyika mabhisikiti muparafini.

0:06:43.780,0:06:46.280
Ndisati ndaziva, ndainge ndakutsenga ndichinakirwa nayo.

0:06:46.280,0:06:50.240
Mushure meizvozvo, handaizodya zvokudya zvakawanda ndoenda kunorara.

0:06:50.240,0:06:56.520
zvakaramba zvichienderera mberi. Mhuri yangu yaizviziva zvose ndakanga ndisisagoni kuzvivanza zvakare.

0:06:56.520,0:06:58.960
Pakanga pasina chinhu chavaigona kuita nezvazvo.

0:06:58.960,0:07:02.380
Ndakaedza kurega ndoga asi zvaisakwanisika.

0:07:02.380,0:07:06.760
Ndakaedza, kunyengetera ne zvose. Handaikwanisa kurega.

0:07:06.760,0:07:15.880
Pandakaona vanhu vazhinji vachidzikinurwa pa Emmanuel TV kubva kuzvinhu zvose zvakavapinda muropa,

0:07:15.880,0:07:21.440
Ndakati kwandiri, "Ndinofanira kuenda ikoko kuitira kuti tsika iyi igone kurega".

0:07:21.440,0:07:28.260
Saka ndakauya pano muna January 2012.

0:07:28.260,0:07:35.840
Munhu wa Mwari akakumbira mumwe munhu kuti ashumire Anointing Water pandiri.

0:07:35.840,0:07:38.500
Izvozvo zvakaitwa uye ndakanunurwa.

0:07:38.500,0:07:45.400
Hanzvadzi dzangu ne vakoma, mushure maizvozvo, rudo, chido chikuru che parafini chakafa.

0:07:45.400,0:07:47.960
Pose pandaiiona, ndaiivenga.

0:07:47.960,0:07:54.380
Mwedzi miviri mushure meizvozvo, ndakasangana nemurume wangu tichibva taroorana.

0:07:54.380,0:07:58.400
Mushure meizvozvo, ndakava nemwana. Rumbidzai Ishe!

0:07:58.400,0:08:01.100
Rumbidzai Ishe!

0:08:01.100,0:08:05.980
Saka, madhamu, mungatiudza here - ndeapi matambudziko amaiva nawo pamaive muchiri

0:08:05.980,0:08:09.960
nenhomba muropa yekunwa ne kufunhidza parafini panguva iyoyo?

0:08:09.960,0:08:13.980
Zvinetso zvandaipfuura mazviri ndezvizvi: Ndaiwanzoda kuva ndoga.

0:08:13.980,0:08:19.500
Ndakanga ndiri ndega ndega kusina vamwe vanhu nokuti zvakanga zvisiri zvinoitwa.

0:08:19.500,0:08:22.140
Ndaifunga kuti ndaizvivanza.

0:08:22.140,0:08:26.420
Ndaiwanzoda kuva ndiri ndoga kuitira kuti ndikwanise kuramba ndichiita chiito ichocho.

0:08:26.420,0:08:29.740
Pamusoro paizvozvo, ndaigara ndichirwadziwa ne mudumbu.

0:08:29.740,0:08:32.160
Utano hwangu hwakakanganiswa.

0:08:32.160,0:08:38.100
Zvinoratidza kuti kusunungurwa kwako , minyengetero yako yemakore akawanda haina kurasika.

0:08:38.100,0:08:43.940
Jesu Kristu apindura minyengetero yako kuburikidza ne New Morning Water.

0:08:43.940,0:08:49.220
Iwe ungati chii pamusoro pe Morning Water iyo Mwari akashandisa kukudzikinura?

0:08:49.220,0:08:55.360
Morning Water yakafanana neropa ra Jesu.

0:08:55.360,0:09:01.800
Pandakafafaidzwa ne Morning Water , ndakanzwa getsi richimhanya kose mandiri, semoto.

0:09:01.800,0:09:05.140
Ichokwadi, ndiyo mhinduro ya nhasi.

0:09:05.140,0:09:09.580
Ameni. Zvechokwadi, Jesu Kristu anoshandisa nzira iyi kuti aunze kuporesa,

0:09:09.580,0:09:13.220
kununurwa uye zvikomborero zvose zva Mwari muhupenyu hwevanhu vake.

0:09:13.220,0:09:14.800
Emanueri! (Mwari Anesu - Mateo 1:23)

0:09:14.800,0:09:17.340
Mangwanani akanaka, Chechi.

0:09:17.340,0:09:20.300
Ndangouya pano kuti nditende Ishe

0:09:20.300,0:09:24.420
nokuda kwokudzikinurwa kwemudzimai wangu tisati taroorana.

0:09:24.420,0:09:28.360
Apo patakanga tichigadzirira (kuroorana) ne zvose, akatsanangura kwandiri

0:09:28.360,0:09:33.740
kuti iyi ndiyo yaiva nyaya yaive apfuura nemairi kwemakore akawanda.

0:09:33.740,0:09:42.440
Akashanyira SCOAN uye Mwari mune tsitsi dzake dzisingaperi akamushanyira ndokumununura

0:09:42.440,0:09:46.460
kubva pakutambudzika ikoko kwemakore gumi nemasere sezvatakaoona.

0:09:46.460,0:09:48.560
Zvirokwazvo takaroorana.

0:09:48.560,0:09:57.440
Pakanga pasina dambudziko rakadaro muhupenyu hwedu uye iye akanaka zvakakwana.

0:09:57.440,0:10:00.800
Rumbidzai Ishe! Uchirirai Jesu Kristu!

0:10:00.800,0:10:07.380
Nderipi shoko raunaro kune vanhu kunze uko vari kutambura nemamiriro akafanana?

0:10:07.380,0:10:13.900
Vana va Mwari, pose paunenge uchipfuura nemudambudziko ripi neripi, hazvinei kuti chii,

0:10:13.900,0:10:19.200
Chinhu chakanakisisa chekuita panguva iyoyo ndechokumhanyira kuna Mwari kuburikidza na Jesu

0:10:19.200,0:10:25.240
nokuti akati muna VaRoma 8:32 kuti Haana kuramba Mwanakomana wake asi akamupa pachena.

0:10:25.240,0:10:29.240
Haangagone here kutipa chero chinhu chatinoda?

0:10:29.240,0:10:34.980
Dzikinuro ndiyo yaunoda here? iBudiriro here? Kuporeswa here?

0:10:34.980,0:10:40.440
Munhu akakodzera kumhanyira kwaari ndi Mwari kuburikidza na Jesu uyo anogona kukununura.

0:10:40.440,0:10:43.420
kana kukupa chero chinhu chaunoda panguva iyoyo. Rumbidzai Ishe!

